{"article_id":"CmUM64qyhyye9U2K","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump openly fought with the top two Democratic lawmakers in the Oval Office on Tuesday about government funding ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"throwing into question whether a deal","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to avert a government shutdown","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"was possible ahead of a deadline next week .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"In a remarkable public argument ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"the likes of which is seldom seen before cameras ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Trump brawled with U.S. Senate Democratic Leader Chuck Schumer and House Democratic Leader Nancy Pelosi about paying for a wall on the U.S.-Mexico border","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that they see as ineffective and wasteful .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"\" If we don ' t get what we want , one way or the other","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"- whether it ' s through you , through a military , through anything","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"you want to call -","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"I will shut down the government , \"","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"as the heated argument drew to a crescendo .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"\" I am proud to shut down the government for border security , Chuck ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"because the people of this country don ' t want criminals and people","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"that have lots of problems and drugs","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"pouring into our country , \"","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"before reporters left their ringside seats .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence sat beside Trump , silent and stone faced .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"While Trump ' s fellow Republicans control both the House and the Senate until next month ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Democratic support is needed","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"to pass any spending legislation .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"If the impasse can not be resolved by Dec. 21 ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"about one-quarter of the federal government immediately would be left without funding .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"Money for the rest of the government already has been appropriated .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Trump has asked Congress for $ 5 billion for border security ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"while Schumer and Pelosi have offered to extend funding at current levels , around $ 1.3 billion .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"That is less than the $ 1.6 billion","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"a bipartisan Senate committee approved .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"While the battle over border security is contentious ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"the money","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"being negotiated","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"is a small portion of a $ 450 billion bill","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"to keep agencies operating through next September .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"In an interview with later in the day , Trump did not rule out a compromise on the funding .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"\" We have to see what else is entailed , \"","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"The meeting did not last long","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"after reporters were ushered out of the Oval Office .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"But the harsh words continued during a closed meeting of House Democrats .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"According to an aide in the room ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Pelosi said","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"Trump ' s fixation with building a wall was \" like a manhood thing for him .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"As if manhood could ever be associated with him . \"","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Pelosi told reporters","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"she had asked Trump to pray about resolving the dispute ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"recounting the biblical story of King Solomon","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"asking God for wisdom .","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"Pelosi told reporters","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that later in the day that she and Trump spoke by telephone ,","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"and the president said","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"he was reviewing the offer","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"made by Democrats during the White House meeting .","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"Despite the rancor ,","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , a Republican , told reporters ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" I ' d still like to see a smooth ending here","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and I haven ' t given up hope","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that ' s what we ' ll have . \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump talks with Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"( D-NY )","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"as he meets with the Senate and House Democratic leadership at the White House in Washington , U.S. , December 11 , 2018 .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"/Kevin Lamarque","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"If there is no deal ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Trump would be shuttering the very agency in charge of border security","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"- the Department of Homeland Security .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"In past shutdown battles , workers","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"deemed \" essential \"","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"were instructed to work .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"Other federal agencies","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that also would face closures","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"include the departments of State , Commerce and Agriculture ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"and visitors would not be allowed into federal parks .","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"At the Pentagon , Lieutenant Colonel Jamie Davis said","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"there were no plans now for the U.S. military to build sections of the border wall ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"though the Defense Department could under current law pay for some border barrier projects \" such as in support of counter-drug operations or national emergencies . \"","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"The rocky White House meeting was the first","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"Trump held with Pelosi and Schumer","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"since Democrats won control of the House in Nov. 6 elections ,","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"possibly foreshadowing battles","depth":5},{"id":82,"text":"to come next year .","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"Trump told","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"he thought","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"it would be possible to work on legislation with Democrats","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"- unless they launch a barrage of investigations into his administration and policies .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"\" We ' re either going to start the campaign","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"and they ' re going to do presidential harassment .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Or we ' re going to get tremendous amounts of legislation passed","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"working together , \"","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"Tuesday ' s fight kicked off","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"when Pelosi told Trump","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"that Americans did not want to see a \" Trump shutdown , \" touching a nerve .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"Trump cut off Pelosi ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"arguing","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"that he could not advance a funding bill","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"without Democratic votes in the Senate .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"\" If I needed the votes for the wall in the House ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"I would have them in one session .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"It would be done , \"","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"Trump bragged .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"\" Well then - go do it ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"go do it , \"","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Pelosi shot back .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"Senior White House staff watched the melee from the edges of the room .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"we should have a debate in front of the press on this , \"","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Pelosi said ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"adding ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"\" Let ' s call a halt to this . \"","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"\" It ' s not bad , Nancy -","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"it ' s called transparency , \"","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":229,"left":0,"right":228,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":228,"left":191,"right":227,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":174,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":135,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":118,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":1,"right":117,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":116,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":116,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":133,"right":21,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":121,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":119,"right":120,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":119,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":126,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":124,"right":125,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":12,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":9,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":13,"righ